  </m:mrow>
 </m:semantics>
</m:math>, and <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>Q</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mtext>h</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{Q rSub { size 8{h} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>  is given, so the efficiency is</para><equation id="eip-607"><m:math>
